`elasticsearch-query-tookit`是一款基于SQL查询elasticsearch编程工具包，支持SQL解析生成DSL，支持JDBC驱动，支持和Spring、MyBatis集成，提供Java编程接口可基于此工具包二次开发
 
[b]只是重新造了个轮子，有兴趣的同学可以相互交流，QQ: 465360798[/b]
 
项目地址：[url]https://github.com/gitchennan/elasticsearch-query-toolkit[/url]
 
[b]一、SQL解析生成DSL使用示例[/b]
SQL语法帮助手册戳这里: [url]https://github.com/gitchennan/elasticsearch-query-toolkit/wiki/elasticsearch-query-toolkit-help-doc[/url]
 
[code]String sql = &quot;select * from index.order where status='SUCCESS' and price &gt; 100 order by nvl(pride, 0) asc routing by 'JD' limit 0, 20&quot;;

